CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,FDuring a busy day on the Isle of Man,
OL,7,Fwhere he holds the title Lord of Mann,
OL,8,Fthe King enjoyed a ride on a horse-
OL,9,Fdrawn tram along Douglas promenade and
OL,10,Fattended a garden party.
OL,12,FCharles visited Tynwald, the world's
OL,13,Foldest continuous parliament, for a
OL,14,Fformal welcome to this self-governing
OL,15,FCrown dependency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,FWelcoming parliamentarians, he
OL,7,Freferenced this year's "Manx Language
OL,8,FYear ` Blein ny Gaelgey," before
OL,9,Fraising a laugh as he said: "So I very
OL,10,Fmuch hope I have not succeeded at this
OL,11,Fpoint in massacring this wonderful
OL,12,Fcelebration of your language...!"
OL,14,FHe continued to say: "As the world's
OL,15,Foldest parliament in continuous
OL,16,Foperation, Tynwald holds a remarkable
OL,17,Fdistinction,
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@YO]qD@]OUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,F"This longevity speaks not only to the
OL,7,Fstrength of your institutions, but
OL,8,Falso of the enduring partnership
OL,9,Fbetween the Crown and the people of
OL,10,Fthis Island."
OL,12,FHe also reflected on royal history and
OL,13,Fsaid: "The first Royal visit was by my
OL,14,Fgreat great great grandfather, Prince
OL,15,FAlbert, who was rowed ashore from the
OL,16,Fsteam-driven Royal Yacht, Victoria And
OL,17,FAlbert in September 1847, disembarked
OL,18,Fat Ramsey, and became the first Royal
OL,19,Fvisitor to the Island."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]uD@GOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,FAfter the formalities, Charles met the
OL,7,Fpublic outside Tynwald, shaking hands
OL,8,Fand exchanging words with well-wishers.
OL,10,FAmong them was Fabienne Favray,
OL,11,Foriginally from France but now a Manx
OL,12,Fresident, who enjoyed a brief
OL,13,Fconversation with the King in her
OL,14,Fnative French.
OL,16,FOn Douglas' seafront, Charles marked
OL,17,Fthe 150th anniversary of the city's
OL,18,Fhorse-drawn tram service by taking a
OL,19,Fride on a recently restored double-
OL,20,Fdecker tram, waving to crowds lining
OL,21,Fthe route.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,FHe also spoke with members of the
OL,7,Frestoration team and Peter Cannon, the
OL,8,Ftram service's longest-serving member,
OL,9,Fwho has worked there for 51 years.
OL,11,FLater, the King chatted with 104-year-
OL,12,Fold Burma Star veteran James Fenton,
OL,13,Fsharing a laugh about getting older,
OL,14,FCharles joked "It's terrible because
OL,15,Fbits keep dropping off,"
OL,26,@vD@OOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
