OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784207920
OL,3,CKing shows off language skills during
OL,4,CIsle of Man visit
OL,6,FThe two men, who met last year at the
OL,7,FVJ Day 80th anniversary in London,
OL,8,Fwere reunited at Port Soderick Beach
OL,9,Fat the Heroes On The Water Isle of Man
OL,10,Fcharity, which offers kayak angling to
OL,11,Finjured military and uniformed
OL,12,Fservices personnel.
OL,14,FThe visit was a celebration of the
OL,15,FIsle of Man's unique culture,
OL,16,Flanguage, and community spirit,
OL,17,Fshowcased by a monarch happy to
OL,18,Fembrace the island's magic, history,
OL,19,Fand people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
